window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Vehicles, suddenly unmanned, careen out of control. People are terror-stricken as loved ones vanish before their eyes. In the midst of global chaos, airline captain Rayford Steele must search for his family, for answers, for truth. As devastating as the disappearances have been, the darkest days may lie ahead.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The moving <i>Left Behind</i> series, from the popular Christian authors Tim LaHaye and Jerry B. Jenkins, offers an account of what life might be like for those left behind when millions vanish.</p>"; 
